defs.name: Call
defs.value:
pub enum Call<T: Trait> {

    #[doc(hidden)]
    #[codec(skip)]
    __PhantomItem(::frame_support::sp_std::marker::PhantomData<(T,)>,
                  ::frame_support::Never),

    #[allow(non_camel_case_types)]
    submit_price(u32),

    #[allow(non_camel_case_types)]
    submit_price_unsigned(T::BlockNumber, u32),

    #[allow(non_camel_case_types)]
    submit_price_unsigned_with_signed_payload(PricePayload<T::Public,
                                                           T::BlockNumber>,
                                              T::Signature),
}
